(1711, 1, '2026-03-24 16:54:49', '2026-03-24 16:54:49', '<h1>Services</h1>				\n				<h3 data-elementor-setting-key=\\\"infocard_title\\\" data-elementor-inline-editing-toolbar=\\\"basic\\\" >Web Design</h3>			\n					We create custom web design for small businesses, this will help you capture new audiences and increase your sales. Contact us by calling, emailing or filling out our form. You will receive a free quote by email within 24 hours.				\n					<a href=\\\"#\\\">\n									Explore\n					</a>\n															<img width=\\\"1024\\\" height=\\\"811\\\" src=\\\"https://websitedemos.net/earth-02/wp-content/uploads/sites/1125/2022/10/Web-Design-1024x811.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" srcset=\\\"https://websitedemos.net/earth-02/wp-content/uploads/sites/1125/2022/10/Web-Design-1024x811.jpg 1024w, https://websitedemos.net/earth-02/wp-content/uploads/sites/1125/2022/10/Web-Design-300x238.jpg 300w, https://websitedemos.net/earth-02/wp-content/uploads/sites/1125/2022/10/Web-Design-768x608.jpg 768w, https://websitedemos.net/earth-02/wp-content/uploads/sites/1125/2022/10/Web-Design-600x475.jpg 600w, https://websitedemos.net/earth-02/wp-content/uploads/sites/1125/2022/10/Web-Design-400x317.jpg 400w, https://websitedemos.net/earth-02/wp-content/uploads/sites/1125/2022/10/Web-Design.jpg 1134w\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\\\" />															\n															<img width=\\\"1024\\\" height=\\\"806\\\" src=\\\"https://websitedemos.net/earth-02/wp-content/uploads/sites/1125/2022/10/Graphic-Design-1024x806.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" srcset=\\\"https://websitedemos.net/earth-02/wp-content/uploads/sites/1125/2022/10/Graphic-Design-1024x806.jpg 1024w, https://websitedemos.net/earth-02/wp-content/uploads/sites/1125/2022/10/Graphic-Design-300x236.jpg 300w, https://websitedemos.net/earth-02/wp-content/uploads/sites/1125/2022/10/Graphic-Design-768x604.jpg 768w, https://websitedemos.net/earth-02/wp-content/uploads/sites/1125/2022/10/Graphic-Design-600x472.jpg 600w, https://websitedemos.net/earth-02/wp-content/uploads/sites/1125/2022/10/Graphic-Design-400x315.jpg 400w, https://websitedemos.net/earth-02/wp-content/uploads/sites/1125/2022/10/Graphic-Design.jpg 1141w\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\\\" />															\n				<h3 data-elementor-setting-key=\\\"infocard_title\\\" data-elementor-inline-editing-toolbar=\\\"basic\\\" >Graphic Design</h3>			\n					We specialize in logos, merchandise and more. Anyone can create nice graphics but it’s much better to create memorable ones. Contact us by calling, emailing or filling out our form. You will receive a free quote by email within 24 hours.				\n					<a href=\\\"#\\\">\n									Explore\n					</a>\n				<h3 data-elementor-setting-key=\\\"infocard_title\\\" data-elementor-inline-editing-toolbar=\\\"basic\\\" >Content Writing</h3>			\n					Want to attract people to your website? You have to have the best content in the world. Our content writers will create award willing content for you. Contact us by calling, emailing or filling out our form. You will receive a free quote by email within 24 hours.				\n					<a href=\\\"#\\\">\n									Explore\n					</a>\n															<img width=\\\"1024\\\" height=\\\"811\\\" src=\\\"https://websitedemos.net/earth-02/wp-content/uploads/sites/1125/2022/10/Content-Writing-1024x811.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" srcset=\\\"https://websitedemos.net/earth-02/wp-content/uploads/sites/1125/2022/10/Content-Writing-1024x811.jpg 1024w, https://websitedemos.net/earth-02/wp-content/uploads/sites/1125/2022/10/Content-Writing-300x238.jpg 300w, https://websitedemos.net/earth-02/wp-content/uploads/sites/1125/2022/10/Content-Writing-768x608.jpg 768w, https://websitedemos.net/earth-02/wp-content/uploads/sites/1125/2022/10/Content-Writing-600x475.jpg 600w, https://websitedemos.net/earth-02/wp-content/uploads/sites/1125/2022/10/Content-Writing-400x317.jpg 400w, https://websitedemos.net/earth-02/wp-content/uploads/sites/1125/2022/10/Content-Writing.jpg 1134w\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\\\" />															\n				<h2 data-elementor-setting-key=\\\"infocard_title\\\" data-elementor-inline-editing-toolbar=\\\"basic\\\" >Talk to us</h2>			\n					Have any questions? We are always open to talk about your business, new projects, creative opportunities and how we can help you.				\n					<a href=\\\"#\\\">\n									Get In Touch\n					</a>', 'Dịch vụ', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'services', '', '', '2026-03-24 17:01:56', '2026-03-24 17:01:56', '', 0, 'http://localhost/thaolinhmateco/services/', 0, 'page', '', 0);
